quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  35,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  35,1,"tareef Allah hi ke liye hai jo asmano aur zameen ka bananay wala aur firshton ko pegham rasan muqarrar kar ne wala hai, ( aisay farishtay ) jin ke do do aur teen teen aur chaar chaar baazu hain woh apni makhlooq ki saakht mein jaissa chahta hai izafah karta hai yaqeenan Allah har cheez par Qadir hai"
  35,2,Allah jis rehmat ka darwaaza bhi logon ke liye khol day usay koi roknay wala nahi aur jisay woh band kar day usay Allah ke baad phir koi dosra kholnay wala nahi woh zabardast aur hakeem hai
  35,3,"logo, tum par Allah ke jo ehsanaat hain inhen yaad rakho kya Allah ke siwa koi aur khaaliq bhi hai jo tumhe aasman aur zameen se rizaq deta ho? koi mabood uss ke siwa nahi, aakhir tum kahan se dhoka kha rahay ho ?"
  35,4,"ab agar ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) yeh log tumhe jutlatay hain ( to yeh koi nai baat nahi ), tum se pehlay bhi bohat se rasooljhutla-ay ja chuke hain, aur saaray mamlaat aakhir kaar Allah hi ki taraf rujoo honay walay hain"
  35,5,"logo, Allah ka wada yaqeenan barhaq hai, lehaza duniya ki zindagi tumhe dhokay mein nah daaley aur nah woh bara dhokay baz tumhe Allah ke baray mein dhoka dainay paye"
  35,6,Dur haqeeqat shetan tumhara dushman hai is liye tum bhi usay apna dushman hi samjhoo woh to apne pairwoon ko apni raah par is liye bulaa raha hai ke woh dozakhyon mein shaamil ho jayen
  35,7,jo log kufar karen ge unn ke liye sakht azaab hai aur jo imaan layein ge aur naik amal karen ge unn ke liye mughfirat aur bara ajar hai
  35,8,( bhala kuch thikana hai uss shakhs ki gumraahi ka ) jis ke liye uss ka bura amal khushnuma bana diya gaya ho aur woh ussay acha samajh raha ho? haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah jisay chahta hai gumraahi mein daal deta hai aur jisay chahta hai raah raast dikha deta hai pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) khuwa makhuwa tumhari jaan un logon ki khatir gham o afsos mein nah ghulay jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain Allah uss ko khoob jaanta hai
  35,9,"woh Allah hi to hai jo hawaon ko bhejta hai, phir woh baadal athati hain, phir hum usay aik ujaar ilaqay ki taraf le jatay hain aur isi zameen ko jِla uthatay hain jo meri pari thi marey hue insanon ka jee uthna bhi isi terhan hoga"
  35,10,"jo koi izzat chahta ho ussay maloom hona chahiye ke izzat saari ki saari Allah ki hai uss ke haan jo cheez oopar chadhti hai woh sirf pakeeza qoul hai, aur amal Saleh is ko oopar chadata hai rahay woh log jo behooda chaal bazyan karte hain, unn ke liye sakht azaab hai aur unn ka makr khud hi ghaarat honay wala hai"
  35,11,"Allah ne tum ko matti se peda kya, phir nutfa se, phir tumahray jore bana diye ( yani mard aur aurat ) koi aurat haamla nahi hoti aur nah bacha janati hai magar yeh sab kuch Allah ke ilm mein hota hai koi Umar panay wala Umar nahi paata aur nah kisi ki Umar mein kuch kami hoti hai magar yeh sab kuch aik kitaab mein likha hota hai Allah ke liye yeh bohat aasaan kaam hai"
  35,12,"aur pani ke dono zakheeray yaksaa nahi hain aik meetha aur pyaas bujhanay wala hai, peenay mein Khushgawar , aur dosra sakht khaari ke halaq chheel day magar dono se tum tar o taaza gosht haasil karte ho, pahannay ke liye zeenat ka samaan nikaltay ho, aur isi pani mein tum dekhte ho ke kashtiyan uss ka seenah cheerti chali ja rahi hain taakay tum Allah ka fazl talaash karo aur uss ke shukar guzaar bano"
  35,13,woh din ke andar raat ko aur raat ke andar din ko pirota howa le aata hai chaand aur Sooraj ko uss ne maskhar kar rakha hai yeh sab kuch aik waqt muqarrar taq chalay ja raha hai wohi Allah ( jis ke yeh saaray kaam hain ) tumhara rab hai badshahi isi ki hai ussay chore kar jin dosaron ko tum pukarte ho woh aik prkah ke maalik bhi nahi hain
  35,14,inhen poukaro to woh tumhari duayen sun nahi satke aur sun len to un ka tumhe koi jawab nahi day satke aur qayamat ke roz woh tumahray shirk ka inkaar kar den ge haqeeqat haal ki aisi sahih khabar tumhe aik khabardaar ke siwa koi nahi day sakta
  35,15,"logo, tum hi Allah ke mohtaaj ho aur Allah to ghanni o hammeed hai"
  35,16,woh chahay to tumhe hata kar koi nai khalqat tumhari jagah le aeye
  35,17,aisa karna Allah ke liye kuch bhi dushwaar nahi
  35,18,koi boojh uthany wala kisi dosray ka boojh nah uthaye ga aur agar koi lada howa nafs apna boojh uthany ke liye pukare ga to is ke baar ka aik adna hissa bhi btane ke liye koi nah aeye ga chahay woh qareeb tareen rishta daar hi kyun nah ho ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum sirf unhi logon ko mutnabba kar satke ho jo be dekhe apne rab se drtay hain aur namaz qaim karte hain jo shakhs bhi pakizgee ikhtiyar karta hai apni hi bhalai ke liye karta hai aur palatna sab ko Allah hi ki taraf hai
  35,19,andha aur aankhon wala barabar nahi hai
  35,20,nah tarikhiyan aur roshni yaksaa hain
  35,21,nah thandhi chaon aur dhoop ki tapish aik jaisi hai
  35,22,"aur nah زندے aur murdy masawi hain Allah jisay chahta hai سنواتا hai, magar ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum unn logon ko nahi suna satke jo qabron mein madfoon hain"
  35,23,tum to bas aik khabardaar karne walay ho
  35,24,hum ne tum ko haq ke sath bheja hai basharat dainay wala aur darane wala bana kar aur koi ummat aisi nahi guzri hai jis mein koi mutnabba karne wala nah aaya ho
  35,25,ab agar yeh log tumhe jutlatay hain to inn se pehlay guzray hue log bhi jhutla chuke hain unn ke paas un ke rasool khulay dalail aur saheefay aur roshan Hadayat dainay wali kitaab le kar aeye thay
  35,26,phir jin logon ne nah maana unn ko mein ne pakar liya aur dekh lau ke meri saza kaisi sakht thi
  35,27,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah aasman se pani barsata hai aur phir is ke zareya se hum terhan terhan ke phal nikaal laatay hain jin ke rang mukhtalif hotay hain pahoron mein bhi safaid, surkh aur gehri siyah daharian payi jati hain jin ke rang mukhtalif hotay hain"
  35,28,aur isi terhan insanon aur janwaron aur maweshion ke rang bhi mukhtalif hain haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ke bundon mein se sirf ilm rakhnay walay log hi uss se drtay hain be shak Allah zabardast aur dar guzar frmane wala hai
  35,29,"jo log kitaab Allah ki talawat karte hain aur namaz qaim karte hain, aur jo kuch hum ne unhen rizaq diya hai is mein se khulay aur chupay kharch karte hain, yaqeenan woh aik aisi tijarat ke mutawaqqa hain jis mein hargiz khasara nah hoga"
  35,30,( is tijarat mein unhon ne apna sab kuch iss liye khappaya hai ) taakay Allah unn ke ajar poooray ke poooray unn ko day aur mazeed apne fazl se un ko ataa farmaiye be shak Allah bakhsnay wala aur qadar daan hai
  35,31,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) jo kitaab hum ne tumhari taraf wahi ke zareya se bhaije hai wohi haq hai, tasdeeq karti hui aayi hai unn kitabon ki jo iss se pehlay aayi theen be shak Allah apne bundon ke haal se bakhabar hai aur har cheez par nigah rakhnay wala hai"
  35,32,"phir hum ne is kitaab ka waris bana diya unn logon ko jinhein hum ne ( iss waarsat ke liye ) apne bundon mein se chunn liya ab koi to un mein se apne nafs par zulm karne wala hai, aur koi beech ki raas hai, aur koi Allah ke azan se nakiyon mein Sabqat karne wala hai, yahi bohat bara fazl hai"
  35,33,"hamesha rehne wali jannaten hain jin mein yeh log daakhil hon ge wahan inhen sonay ke kanganon aur motiyon se aaraasta kya jaye ga, wahan un ka libaas resham hoga"
  35,34,"aur woh kahin ge ke shukar hai uss khuda ka jis ne hum se gham daur kar diya, yaqeenan hamara rab maaf karne wala aur qader frmane wala hai"
  35,35,"jis ne hamein apne fazl se abdi qiyam ki jagahtehra diya, ab yahan nah hamein koi mushaqqat paish aati hai aur nah takan la-haq hoti hai"
  35,36,aur jin logon ne kufar kya hai unn ke liye jahannum ki aag hai nah unn ka qissa pak kar diya jaye ga ke mar jayen aur nah unn ke liye jahannum ke azaab mein koi kami ki jaye gi iss terhan hum badla dete hain har uss shakhs ko jo kufar karne wala ho
  35,37,"woh wahan cheekh cheekh kar kahin ge ke"" ae hamaray rab, hamein yahan se nikaal le taakay hum naik amal karen unn aamaal se mukhtalif jo pehlay karte rahay thay"" ( inhen jawab diya jaye ga )"" kya hum ne tum ko itni Umar nah di thi jis mein koi sabaq lena chahta to sabaq le sakta thaا? aur tumahray paas mutnabba karne wala bhi aa chuka tha ab maza chako zaalmon ka yahan koi madadgaar nahi hai """
  35,38,"be shak Allah asmano aur zameen ki har posheeda cheez se waaqif hai, woh to seenon ke chupay hue raaz taq jaanta hai"
  35,39,"wohi to hai jis ne tum ko zameen mein khalifa banaya hai ab jo koi kufar karta hai is ke kufar ka wabaal usi par hai, aur kafiroon ko unn ka kufar iss ke siwa koi taraqqi nahi deta ke un ke rab ka ghazab unn par ziyada se ziyada bharakta chala jata hai kafiroon ke liye khasaray mein izafay ke siwa koi taraqqi nahi"
  35,40,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) un se kaho,"" kabhi tum ne dekha bhi hai apne unn sharikon ko jinhein tum khuda ko chore kar puraka karte ho? mujhe batao, unhon ne zameen mein kya peda kya hai? ya asmano mein un ki kya shirkat hai""? ( agar yeh nahi bta satke to un se pucho ) kya hum ne inhen koi tehreer likh kar di hai jis ki bana par yeh ( apne is shirk ke liye ) koi saaf sanad rakhtay hon? nahi, balkay yeh zalim aik dosray ko mehez fraib ke jhansey diye ja rahay hain"
  35,41,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah hi hai jo asmano aur zameen ko tal jaane se rokay hue hai, aur agar woh tal jayen to Allah ke baad koi dosra inhen thaamnay wala nahi hai be shak Allah bara Haleem aur dar guzar frmane wala hai"
  35,42,yeh log kari kari kasmain kha kar kaha karte thay ke agar koi khabardaar karne wala un ke haan aa gaya hota to yeh duniya ki har doosri qoum se barh kar raast ro hotay magar jab khabardaar karne wala un ke paas agaya to is ki aamad ne inn ke andar haq se faraar ke siwa kisi cheez mein izafah nah kya
  35,43,"yeh zameen mein aur ziyada اistakbar karne lagey aur buri buri chaalein chalne lagey, halaank burii chaalein apne chalne walon hi ko le bithti hain ab kya yeh log iss ka intzaar kar rahay hain ke pichli qomon ke sath Allah ka jo tareeqa raha hai wohi inn ke sath bhi brta jaye? yahi baat hai to tum Allah ke tareeqay mein hargiz koi tabdeeli nah pao ge aur tum kabhi nah dekho ge ke Allah ki sunnat ko is ke muqarrar rastay se koi taaqat phair sakti hai"
  35,44,"kya yeh log zameen mein kabhi chalay phiray nahi hain ke inhen unn logon ka injaam nazar aata jo inn se pehlay guzar chuke hain aur un se bohat ziyada taaqat war thay? Allah ko koi cheez aajiz karne wali nahi hai, nah asmano mein aur nah zameen mein woh sab kuch jaanta hai aur har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  35,45,agar kahin woh logon ko unn ke kiye krtoton par pokarta to zameen par kisi mutnaqas ko jeeta nah chhorta magar woh inhen aik muqarrar waqt taq ke liye mohlat day raha hai phir jab un ka waqt aan poora hoga to Allah apne bundon ko dekh le ga
